The air ambulance was scrambled to a "medical emergency" on the motorway. National Highways have asked people to seek alternative routes where possible. The M25 is blocked in both directions in Hertfordshire this afternoon. Traffic stationary due to a medical emergency between J21 M1 J6A and J20 A41 Watford Road, Kings Langley. INRIX traffic alert system reports: "M25 in both directions is blocked. "There is stationary traffic due to medical emergency between J21 M1 J6A and J20 A41 Watford Road (Kings Langley). "Air ambulance is at the scene of the problem." 